imdb.plot outline: Follows interior design matchmaker Lloyd Princeton as he introduces his clients, Grammy-winning producer Tricky Stewart and his wife, to three interior designers who then must compete to make over their guest bedroom and bathroom. Designers Charles Neal, Julia Wong and Jessica Bennett each present their concepts to the homeowners who decide which designer best articulates their aesthetics and personalities. However, the Stewarts begin to question their choice when the selected designer doesn't adhere to their timetable and budget.
